post_text:
Please share with families in need:

If you don't already have internet, students can get 60 days of FREE internet from Spectrum so they can keep learning while school buildings are closed. Call 1-855-243-8892 to schedule installation.

Please call Spectrum for details, but qualifications, as we understand, are:
* New service customers only;
* Used for remote learning only;
* 2 months free, no contract
* Promo rate of $54.98 after 2 months, cancel anytime and no prepayments;
* If household has a previous 'past due' balance, that needs to be paid prior to signing up;
* Self-install kits will be sent or, if household requires professional installation, those fees are waived;
* 100-200 Mbps per second;
* Families can go to https://www.spectrum.com/ to see if their address is served by Spectrum.

